<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id7703df83-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s110b"><num value="110b">§ 110b.</num><heading> Administration of headquarters site</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The headquarters site provided pursuant to <ref href="/us/usc/t16/s110a">section 110a of this title</ref> shall constitute a part of Mount Rainier National Park and be administered in accordance with the laws applicable thereto.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id7703df84-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/86/521/s2">Pub. L. 86–521, § 2</ref>, <date date="1960-06-27">June 27, 1960</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/74/219">74 Stat. 219</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
